      &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">href</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;cart.html&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;Sepetim&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">            &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">href</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;signin.html&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;Giriş Yap&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">div</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">header</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Sıradaki işlem headera şekil vermek olacak. </p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai\" data-language=\"css\" data-index=\"8\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk5\">.header</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">grid-area</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: header;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">display</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">flex</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">justify-content</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">space-between</span><span class=\"mtk